metadata.name: Cute girlfriend
metadata.description:
This photo is the first in a new collection. The model is a Japanese woman. She has a great sense of aesthetics and is currently a college student who is widely active as a YouTuber, dancer and talent. This work is a work that pursues coolness while sticking to costumes and being sexy. Even if it's sexy, I want to express the attractiveness of women and the coolness of women with photographs.
